arts.ttl: Cameroon, Algeria seal places in AFCON finals
arts.sum: Five-time winners Cameroon and 2019 champions Algeria both booked their places at next year's Africa Cup of Nations finals in Morocco after victories in qualifying on Monday, bringing the number of qualified teams to four.

arts.ttl: Preview: Kenya vs. Cameroon - prediction, team news, lineups
arts.sum: Sports Mole previews Monday's Africa Cup of Nations Qualifying clash between Kenya and Cameroon, including predictions, team news and possible lineups.
